{"tid":1843272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱食完團年飯 有個親戚係美心高層","createTime":"2020-01-26T06:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T06:57:09.000Z","uid":132174,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ea449a56b111fa9fce96d6b5d04360545fb5a9ae","tid":1843272,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:34:46.000Z","msg":"其實就唔係好熟，所以成餐飯都冇人講政治 避重就輕，但係做得美心都知黃定藍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n講講吓佢就話自己負責catering (學校醫院嗰啲飯堂)，話比班學生搞破壞搞到生意好慘淡。我心諗有冇咁厚面皮㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你啲顧客唔鍾意食你啲嘢，調返轉賴人都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n最後仲話我屋企附近有間美心MX，啲嘢幾掂，得閒可以去試吓。本身我成餐飯都冇出過聲，但係嗰刻我勇武巴上身，就咁拋低左句：「唔使啦，我哋屋企食大快活㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢表情係：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果下真係覺得自己幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a1164f83859d3aa415ae304d80b81965d6f080","tid":1843272,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:37:04.000Z","msg":"叻"},{"pid":"e3ed09dce017b17b19588e034c5c90a35868ea7e","tid":1843272,"uid":305802,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:37:37.000Z","msg":"屌美心好撚多黃架on9"},{"pid":"50a0e6c6991205c800a9ce1560d3987aadfba8eb","tid":1843272,"uid":120555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:38:18.000Z","msg":"除佢褲睇下底褲黃唔黃先啦"},{"pid":"aa0689ff23cb72eeb3ca8c7f3f94625caa834ae4","tid":1843272,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ea449a56b111fa9fce96d6b5d04360545fb5a9ae","tid":1843272,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:34:46.000Z","msg":"其實就唔係好熟，所以成餐飯都冇人講政治 避重就輕，但係做得美心都知黃定藍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n講講吓佢